{"tid":2135171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局范鴻齡稱亞博館社區治療設施今啟用","createTime":"2020-08-01T08:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T16:46:27.000Z","uid":353956,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d34159144dbb2a24b110f96b9c3455445b733e94","tid":2135171,"uid":353956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541170-20200801.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541170-20200801.htm&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62Ph6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=769f8397\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541170-20200801.htm&h=82e2531a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541170-20200801.htm</a><br />\n醫管局主席范鴻齡接受《央視》訪問，表示被稱為「方艙醫院」的亞洲博覽館社區治療設施，今日正式啟用，首日預計接收約30名輕症患者，之後再逐步增加。<br />\n<br />\n他說，亞博館會有50名醫護及50名支援人員，整個場館可提供2000個床位，今日率先啟用的一號館有500個，形容一切已準備就緒，至於二號館仍有技術問題，需要解決。<br />\n<br />\n對於中央將派遣內地檢測人員前往香港，協助開展大規模核酸檢測篩查；范鴻齡認為是一個好消息，指現在可以每日做6000個測試，但仍主要面對人手問題，因此中央決定能幫上大忙。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，希望中央可參考內地的模式，派人到香港協助多建幾間臨時醫院，讓病床數目能快速增長。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">仲有條CCTVB 播CCTV范鴻齡訪問既片 真係人唔笑狗都吠</span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gniani3B_VI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dgniani3B_VI&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62Ph6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=f6297f73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gniani3B_VI</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaE1yDa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaE1yDa.png&h=6b38fb58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，國家衞健委亦已組建「內地方艙醫院支援隊」，由湖北武漢選派六名專家，包括醫院院長、護理、建築和設計專家等，為亞博館改建「方艙醫院」提供設計、營運和管理經驗的技術支持。醫管局形容是「幫大忙」。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局主席范鴻齡表示：「主要現在不是試劑的問題，現在是人手的問題，我們的人員已經差不多是24小時工作，最要緊的支持，希望中央能派人到香港，幫我們建立內地模式的臨時醫院，多建幾個，讓病床數目能快速增長。」"},{"pid":"42e0547f59560cf5a2d5786373678e85e4f01b4b","tid":2135171,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:47:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gfzuaGV-lC8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgfzuaGV-lC8&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62Ph6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=c82f057c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gfzuaGV-lC8</a><br />\n全力要求亞博全天侯24小時播"},{"pid":"d0ede920d3e22ab1936299a01a74813b9c0f6cc4","tid":2135171,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:48:08.000Z","msg":"亞洲博覽殯儀館<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167ceca7bea6efb8b0d023dc6cb4d88172c7441f","tid":2135171,"uid":353956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42e0547f59560cf5a2d5786373678e85e4f01b4b","tid":2135171,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:47:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gfzuaGV-lC8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgfzuaGV-lC8&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62Ph6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=c82f057c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gfzuaGV-lC8</a><br />\n全力要求亞博全天侯24小時播"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"你想d人死快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334469387cb7cb7334041765d3223a21e892dfef","tid":2135171,"uid":78047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"一定起得好求其<br />\n覺得之後好多野問題同埋會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba9332af17ef9865184339a942f9182117a67f4","tid":2135171,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:01:18.000Z","msg":"醫咩院，根本係難民營"},{"pid":"b0dae218827bce464ee58197727e9be5bce32b9b","tid":2135171,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fba9332af17ef9865184339a942f9182117a67f4","ti